// 1. Moved the struct Holder above the mapping Acc
// 2. Changed the var to Holder storage in functions Put and Collect
// 3. Removed the external payable modifier from function Collect and replaced it with require statement
// 4. Replaced msg.sender.call.value with msg.sender.transfer in function Collect to prevent reentrancy attack
// 5. Added memory keyword in function AddMessage to fix compilation error
// 6. Added Message memory LastMsg in function AddMessage to fix the bug of all messages being the same